WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.180 --> 00:00:04.180
One task should never be limited to one answer.

2
00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:09.530
Asylum gives every agent an isolated place to work.

3
00:00:10.330 --> 00:00:15.405
Follow progress, inspect context, and keep every attempt visible.

4
00:00:16.205 --> 00:00:21.205
Review what changed. Verify the result. Send precise feedback.

5
00:00:22.005 --> 00:00:25.580
When the evidence is clear, merge the winner.

6
00:00:26.505 --> 00:00:30.105
Parallel work. One confident decision.
